    public class HtmlTemplateExporter

      • export

        public void export(SampleContext context,
                   java.io.File file,
                   ReportGeneratorConfiguration configuration)
            throws ExportException
        从接口复制的说明: DataExporter
        Export data from the specified context using the given configuration.
        参数:
        context - the context (must not be null)
        file - the file which from samples come (must not be null)
        configuration - the configuration (must not be null)
        抛出:
        ExportException - the export exception
